      <title>CentOS安装MySQL</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/07/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/07/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文介绍在CentOS7.9中安装MySQL</p><p>软件环境：VMware17</p><p>系统版本：Windows10（主机），CentOS7.9（虚拟机）</p><p>MySQL版本：MySQL-Community-8.0.26</p><h3 id="查看系统中是否以安装MariaDB"><a href="#查看系统中是否以安装MariaDB" class="headerlink" title="查看系统中是否以安装MariaDB"></a>查看系统中是否以安装MariaDB</h3><p>MariaDB是MySQL的一个分支，从Red Hat Enterprise Linux&#x2F;CentOS 7.0开始已默认不在安装MySQL，而是使用MariaDB代替MySQL；</p><p>使用以下命令查看系统中是否已安装MariaDB：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -qa|grep mariadb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有如下输出则表示系统已经默认安装MariaDB，若无输出，则表示没有安装MariaDB，可跳过卸载步骤；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mariadb-libs-5.5.68-1.el7.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="卸载MariaDB"><a href="#卸载MariaDB" class="headerlink" title="卸载MariaDB"></a>卸载MariaDB</h3><p>使用下列命令删除MariaDB：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -e --nodeps mariadb-libs-5.5.68-1.el7.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者不带版本号：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -e --nodeps mariadb-libs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="下载MySQL安装包"><a href="#下载MySQL安装包" class="headerlink" title="下载MySQL安装包"></a>下载MySQL安装包</h3><p>首先进入<a href="" target="_blank" >MySQL官网</a>，点击上方的下载<code>--&gt;</code>下翻找到MySQL Community (GPL) Downloads，点击跳转到新的页面<code>--&gt;</code>找到MySQL Community Server点击进入下载页面<code>--&gt;</code>点击Archives，进入下载历史版本–&gt;Product Version选择8.0.26<code>--&gt;</code>Operating System选择Red Hat Enterprise Linux &#x2F; Oracle Linux<code>--&gt;</code>OS Version选择Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 &#x2F; oracle Linux 7 (x86,64-bit)<code>--&gt;</code>下方第一项，复制下载链接；</p><img src="/2023/06/07/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL/downloadmysql.png" class="" title="下载MySQL"><p>使用<code>wget</code>命令下载安装包：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://downloads.mysql.com/archives/get/p/23/file/mysql-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm-bundle.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也可以直接通过浏览器下载。</p><h3 id="安装MySQL"><a href="#安装MySQL" class="headerlink" title="安装MySQL"></a>安装MySQL</h3><h4 id="解压"><a href="#解压" class="headerlink" title="解压"></a>解压</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -xvf mysql-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm-bundle.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p>解压得到9个包，其中test是测试包，不需要安装，devel页可以不安装，有两种安装方式；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql-community-client-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-client-plugins-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-common-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-devel-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-embedded-compat-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-libs-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-libs-compat-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-server-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">mysql-community-test-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第一种，按照官方文档，使用一条命令直接安装：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install mysql-community-&#123;server,client,common,libs&#125;-*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二种，按照顺序依次安装：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-common-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-client-plugins-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-libs-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-libs-compat-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-client-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-embedded-compat-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -vih mysql-community-server-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">rpm -ivh mysql-community-devel-8.0.26-1.el7.x86_64.rpm --force --nodeps </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改密码"><a href="#修改密码" class="headerlink" title="修改密码"></a>修改密码</h3><p>首先允许 MySQL开机启动，并启动MySQL：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> mysqld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl status mysqld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看MySQL是否启动，输出inactive表示未启动，activate表示启动，若未启动，则使用下面的命令启动：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl start mysqld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2023/06/07/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL/checkmysql.png" class="" title="查看MySQL是否启动"><p>查看MySQL默认密码：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">grep <span class="string">&#x27;temporary password&#x27;</span> /var/log/mysqld.log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用默认密码登录，修改密码，密码规则：至少包含一个大写字母、一个小写字母，一个数字，一个特殊符号，且总长度至少8个字符；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p</span><br><span class="line">Enter password:<span class="comment">#输入密码</span></span><br><span class="line">mysql&gt;ALTER USER <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span> IDENTIFIED BY <span class="string">&#x27;你的密码&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此，MySQL基本配置完成。</p>]]></content>
      
      
