      <title>CentOS安装tomcat和maven</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文介绍在CentOS7.9中安装Maven和Tomcat</p><p>软件环境：VMware17</p><p>系统版本：Windows 10（主机）、CentOS7.9（虚拟机）</p><p>Maven版本：3.9.0</p><p>Tomcat版本：9.0.75</p><h3 id="安装Tomcat"><a href="#安装Tomcat" class="headerlink" title="安装Tomcat"></a>安装Tomcat</h3><h4 id="下载安装包"><a href="#下载安装包" class="headerlink" title="下载安装包"></a>下载安装包</h4><p>首先去<a href="https://tomcat.apache.org/" target="_blank">Tomcat官网</a>下载安装包，在侧边栏Download下Tomcat9，找到二进制发行版(Binary Distributions)，在tar.gz处右击复制链接，或者直接点击链接下载</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/tomcatDownload.png" class="" title="下载Tomcat"><p>打开CentOS终端，使用wget命令下载，默认下载至当前目录，如果速度很慢，可以使用国内的镜像站下载，这里是从华为镜像站下载的</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 华为源下载</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://repo.huaweicloud.com/apache/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.75/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.75.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下面为从官网下载</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.75/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.75.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果输出错误信息提示证书过期，加上--no-check-certificate参数即可</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/apache/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.75/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.75.tar.gz --no-check-certificate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="解压安装"><a href="#解压安装" class="headerlink" title="解压安装"></a>解压安装</h4><p>下载完成后，使用tar命令将下载的压缩包解压至<code>/usr/local/</code>目录下（位置没有严格要求，个人习惯，<code>/usr/local/</code>是CentOS默认软件安装位置，貌似），解压完成后重命名为tomcat（可选，个人觉得默认目录名太长，看着不舒服）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf apache-tomcat-9.0.75.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> /usr/local/apache-tomcat-9.0.75 /usr/local/tomcat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="测试"><a href="#测试" class="headerlink" title="测试"></a>测试</h4><p>进入<code>/usr/local/tomcat/bin</code>目录，执行<code>startup.sh</code>命令，需要注意的是，启动Tomcat之前，系统需要有Java环境，如果没有配置Java，请转至<a href="/2023/06/05/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjdk1-8/" title="CentOS安装配置jdk1.8">CentOS安装配置jdk1.8</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/local/tomcat/bin</span><br><span class="line">./start.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开浏览器，输入<code>localhost:8080</code>或者<code>ip:8080</code>打开以下页面即表示成功</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/tomcatstart.png" class="" title="启动Tomcat"><h4 id="修改并开放端口（选）"><a href="#修改并开放端口（选）" class="headerlink" title="修改并开放端口（选）"></a>修改并开放端口（选）</h4><p>将Tomcat默认端口号修改为80（HTTP默认端口，直接通过IP地址访问）</p><p>进入<code>/usr/local/tomcat/conf</code>修改server.xml文件，将Connector端口号改为80</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/local/tomcat/conf</span><br><span class="line">vim server.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑完成后按<code>Esc</code>键退出编辑模式然后<code>Shift</code> + <code>;</code> + <code>wq</code>，回车保存退出</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/editport.png" class="" title="修改tomcat端口号"><p>开放80端口，允许其他计算机访问</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 关闭tomcat</span></span><br><span class="line">../bin/shutdown.sh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 开放端口</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --add-port=80/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新加载配置，使更改生效</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新启动tomcat</span></span><br><span class="line">../bin/startup.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在，我们可以不使用段口号直接访问Tomcat</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/visitbyport.png" class="" title="使用IP地址tomcat"><h3 id="安装Maven"><a href="#安装Maven" class="headerlink" title="安装Maven"></a>安装Maven</h3><h4 id="下载Maven"><a href="#下载Maven" class="headerlink" title="下载Maven"></a>下载Maven</h4><p>从<a href="https://maven.apache.org/" target="_blank">Maven官网</a>下载安装包，按照下图指示复制下载链接</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/mavendownload.png" class="" title="下载maven"><p>是用wget命令下载安装包，如果下载速度慢，同样可以使用国内镜像，这里提供华为云下载链接（说来惭愧，我在清华镜像站找不到……）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 华为源</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://repo.huaweicloud.com/apache/maven/maven-3/3.9.0/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.0-bin.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 官网</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/maven/maven-3/3.9.0/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.0-bin.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="解压安装-1"><a href="#解压安装-1" class="headerlink" title="解压安装"></a>解压安装</h4><p>下载完成后，将压缩包解压至<code>/usr/local/</code>目录下，解压完成后重命名为maven</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf apache-maven-3.9.0-bin.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> /usr/local/apache-maven-3.9.0 /usr/local/maven</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="为maven配置环境变量"><a href="#为maven配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="为maven配置环境变量"></a>为maven配置环境变量</h4><p>使用<code>echo</code>命令将配置信息写入<code>profile</code>，并使用<code>source</code>命令使配置生效</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;export MAVEN_HOME=/usr/local/maven&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;export PATH=\$PATH:\$MAVEN_HOME/bin&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者用vim直接编辑profile</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将下面信息追加至文件尾部</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> MAVEN_HOME=/usr/local/maven</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="variable">$PATH</span>:<span class="variable">$MAVEN_HOME</span>/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意，编辑文件时，<code>$</code>符号前是没有反斜杠<code>\</code>的！！！</p><p>编辑完成后按<code>Esc</code>键退出编辑模式然后<code>Shift</code> + <code>;</code> + <code>wq</code>，回车保存退出，输入命令<code>source /etc/profile</code>使配置生效</p><h4 id="检查配置是否生效"><a href="#检查配置是否生效" class="headerlink" title="检查配置是否生效"></a>检查配置是否生效</h4><p>输入<code>mvn -v</code>命令，输出版本信息即表示配置成功</p><img src="/2023/06/06/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85tomcat%E5%92%8Cmaven/checkmaven.png" class="" title="检查maven"><p>如果没有生效，检查以下四点：</p><p>·是否编辑文件时是否多了<code>\</code>，</p><p>·是否使用echo命令写入时少了<code>\</code>，</p><p>·有没有<code>source /etc/profile</code>，</p><p>·是否同时使用两种写入方式</p><p>至此，Tomcat和Maven的安装及其相关配置完成</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> CentOS </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
