      <title>CentOS安装配置jdk1.8</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/05/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjdk1-8/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/05/CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjdk1-8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文介绍在CentOS7.9中安装Oracle JDK，并配置相关环境变量</p><p>软件环境：VMware17</p><p>系统版本：Windows 10（主机）、CentOS7.9（虚拟机）</p><p>JDK版本：jdk1.8.0_361</p><h3 id="查看系统是否已安装OpenJDK"><a href="#查看系统是否已安装OpenJDK" class="headerlink" title="查看系统是否已安装OpenJDK"></a>查看系统是否已安装OpenJDK</h3><p> 使用命令<code>rpm -qa|grep java</code>查看是否已经安装OpenJDK</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -qa|grep java</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">java-1.8.0-openjdk-headless-1.8.0.262.b10-1.el7.x86_64</span><br><span class="line">python-javapackages-3.4.1-11.el7.noarch</span><br><span class="line">tzdata-java-2020a-1.el7.noarch</span><br><span class="line">javapackages-tools-3.4.1-11.el7.noarch</span><br><span class="line">java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.262.b10-1.el7.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有以上输出即表示系统以安装了OpenJDK，我们需要将其卸载，然后安装Oracle JDK</p><h3 id="卸载OpenJDK"><a href="#卸载OpenJDK" class="headerlink" title="卸载OpenJDK"></a>卸载OpenJDK</h3><p>如果CentOS中已经安装了openjdk，使用<code>rpm -e --nodeps</code>命令卸载，.noarch文件可以不卸载；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -e --nodeps java-1.8.0-openjdk-headless-1.8.0.262.b10-1.el7.x86_64</span><br><span class="line">rpm -e --nodeps java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.262.b10-1.el7.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Oracle-JDK并配置环境变量"><a href="#安装Oracle-JDK并配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="安装Oracle JDK并配置环境变量"></a>安装Oracle JDK并配置环境变量</h3><h4 id="安装jdk"><a href="#安装jdk" class="headerlink" title="安装jdk"></a>安装jdk</h4><p>将下载的jdk压缩包解压至<code>/usr/local/</code>目录下，这里下载的是<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1-L7xXEC-llQ9q8grfo18eg?pwd=vmj9">jdk1.8.0_361</a>版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf jdk-8u361-linux-x64.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> /usr/local</span><br><span class="line">bin  games    jdk1.8.0_361  lib64    maven   sbin   src</span><br><span class="line">etc  include  lib           libexec  share</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解压完成后<code>/usr/local/</code>目录会多出一个<code>jdk1.8.0_361</code>文件夹</p><h4 id="配置环境变量"><a href="#配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="配置环境变量"></a>配置环境变量</h4><p>修改配置文件profile，将jdk加入环境变量；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在文件末尾添加以下信息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/jdk1.8.0_361<span class="comment">#jdk安装目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CLASSPATH=.:<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib:<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib:<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/jre/lib</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="variable">$PATH</span>:<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按<code>Esc</code>退出编辑，<code>Shift + ; + wq</code>保存退出；</p><h4 id="使配置生效"><a href="#使配置生效" class="headerlink" title="使配置生效"></a>使配置生效</h4><p>使用命令<code>source /etc/profile</code>使配置生效，输入命令<code>java -version</code>，输出java版本信息即表示配置成功；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line">java -versuion</span><br><span class="line">java version <span class="string">&quot;1.8.0_361&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.8.0_361-b09)</span><br><span class="line">Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 25.361-b09, mixed mode)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此，Java环境配置完成。</p>]]></content>
      
      
